  "texts": [
    "Additionally, the method suggested is presented comprehensively, including an overview of the integration of multiple CNN models and the approach used to overcome previous limitations.",
    "A graphical representation of the proposed method is also illustrated in Fig 1.",
    "In Fig 1 above, the data preprocessing is described in Section 3.2.",
    "The concatenation after flattening in hybrid models is utilized to combine the outputs from the two models or branches, then introduced to a fully connected network consisting of two dense layers and an output layer with softmax activation.",
    "The dataset utilized in this study was acquired from the Kaggle open-access database, a wellknown platform for machine learning and data science competitions."
  ]
